<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Login Alert</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Login Alert</h1>
    <p>Hello <span style="color: #333; font-weight: bold;">
            <%= username %>
        </span>,</p>

    <p>Your login information was recently accessed on <span style="color: #333;">
            <%= new Date(updatedAt).toLocaleString() %>
        </span>. If you did not perform this action, please take appropriate security measures immediately.</p>

    <p>Here is the information about the login:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>User ID: <span style="color: #333;">
                <%= _id %>
            </span></li>
        <li>Username: <span style="color: #333;">
                <%= username %>
            </span></li>
        <li>Email: <span style="color: #333;">
                <%= email %>
            </span></li>
        <li>Timestamp of Login: <span style="color: #333;">
                <%= new Date(updatedAt).toLocaleString() %>
            </span></li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any concerns or questions regarding this login activity, please contact our support team.</p>

    <p>Thank you for using our service.</p>

    <p>Sincerely,<br>Your Website Team</p>
</body>

</html>